    "en": {
      "title": "This is how the water charges increase",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The gazette notification regarding the increase in water charges has been issued with effect from the first day of September.",
        "Accordingly, the domestic water fee has been raised to 20.00 rupees per unit which was between zero and 05 rupees per unit.",
        "Also, it was stated that the monthly service fee between zero and 05 units which was Rs. 50.00 has been increased to Rs. 300.00.",
        "For water charges above 75 units, the usage fee which was 140 rupees per unit has been increased to 238.00 rupees and the monthly service fee which was 1,600 rupees has been increased to 3,500 rupees under those categories.",
        "In addition to this, other charges and related taxes are included in any category in addition to monthly water charges, usage charges and monthly service charges, according to the relevant gazette notification."
      ],
